  "title": "Want a Job That’s Social, Fun & HIGHLY Rewarding? Join Us!",
  "description": "<p>🚨 ATTENTION Fresh Grads, ORD peeps & career changers — this is not your typical job.<br />If you love interacting with people, have good energy, and want to grow FAST, our Sales & Marketing role is calling your name.</p><p>Zero experience? Perfect.<br />We love fresh energy — we’ll teach you the rest.</p><p>⚡ <strong>Your Daily Experience</strong></p><p>🎉 Events & roadshows that never feel the same<br />🎤 Talking to people, building vibes, making connections<br />🤝 B2B campaigns where you pick up REAL communication skills<br />🔥 Working with a high-energy team that wants to WIN<br />📚 Training that helps you grow from rookie → leader</p><p>💰 <strong>Your Benefits</strong></p><p>💵 Weekly pay + commissions that can go sky-high<br />🏆 Bonuses that reward your grind<br />🚀 Leadership roles for fast learners<br />✈️ Work trips that open your eyes to new experiences<br />🤗 A team culture that feels like family</p><p>🚀 Want a career that motivates you, challenges you, AND makes you excited to show up?<br />Apply now — limited slots available.</p>",
